<td>Install plugin, sitemap auto-generates</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Shopify</td>
<td>Built-in</td>
<td>Auto-generated at <code>/sitemap.xml</code></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Wix</td>
